&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for ensuring the success of our existing customers, owning new initiatives, driving actionable data insights, and growing relationships. You will operate across internal stakeholders to deeply understand our product and play a pivotal role in the product feedback loop based on customer feedback and demand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with our CEO to define success metrics for our customers and advocate for our customers across internal teams. This includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong relationships with our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

