&lt;li&gt;A customer-first mindset, with a passion for making complex solutions feel simple and intuitive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical fluency, including experience working with APIs, SDKs, system integrations, and financial technology solutions (coding experience is not required but is a plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and problem-solving skills, with the ability to connect with clients across industries and levels of technical expertise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project management experience, with the ability to juggle multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A growth mindset—you&#39;re adaptable, eager to learn, and excited about solving new challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with diverse teams and customers, and a commitment to fostering an inclusive environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the outcome, do what it takes to keep merchant implementations on schedule and on track to deliver value to our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;🤝&amp;nbsp;What will you be doing?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
