&lt;li&gt;Provide hands-on support with API and SDK integrations, flow of funds, accounting, system configurations, and wallet launch best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate and empower merchants ensuring they feel confident using our tools and maximizing their value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple projects simultaneously keeping projects on track with internal and external stakeholders informed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion merchant feedback advocating for improvements that make our product more user-friendly and impactful.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do what it takes to get merchants live, on time, with solid integrations which are designed for success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
